claim.claim-text:
A vacuum cosmetic container for cream type cosmetics comprising:
an outer container (100);
an inner container (200), combined at the interior of the outer container (100) and containing contents, inside of which is installed a piston (210) which ascends according to the use of contents;
a support body (300) combined as encircling an upper portion of the outer container (100) and supporting a pumping member (400);
a pumping member (400) combined to the support body (300) and discharging contents by pumping operation;
a button part (500) positioned at an upper portion of the pumping member(400) and pressurizing the pumping member(400), wherein a content movement hole (510) is installed;
a content absorption member (600) positioned at an upper portion of the button part (500) and absorbing contents moving through the content movement hole (510);
a button cap (700) combined as encircling the button part (500) and the content absorption member (600) and delivering pressure to the button part (500) according to a user's pressurizing, wherein a hollow is formed so as for the content absorption member (600) to be exposed to the exterior.
